You lock eyes to eye with Blerk.  You stare into the yellowness of his eye and your mind starts to go blank.  The sounds dim, the lights fade.  You feel like gravity has doubled yet you are also being stretched skyward.  Blerk continues to stare at you.  A twinkle blinks in his eye and you think you see a slight smile curl on his enormous mouth.  All senses fade to black.

You come to feeling refreshed.  Better than you have actually ever felt in your lifetime.  You are euphoric.  Happy.  Eager to please.  Excited about the challenges that await you.  You take a look around to see the loveliness awaiting you.  You scan the room...

WHOA!!!

You see YOU.  Passed out cold like the time your buddies took you to that college party and gave you two beers (well, really a beer and a half, but who's counting).  If that person is you, than who are... you?!?

You look down at yourself and are shocked at what you see.  Like a bad movie, you seem to have switched places with Blerk.

You look back at yourself and cringe.  That's what the ladies see, huh?  Despite that, however, you can't help put succumb to this feeling of pure joy that threatens to overflow.

