You crane your neck and listen, Over the roars of the crowd inside, you can hear a voice.  "As we deal with Mongo now, tomorrow, or tonight, we will find and kill another opposer!"
> e

> e
You summon the courage to venture inside the commons area despite the obvious throng that waits within.  You hope they are distracted by the display not to see through your 'fancy' disguise.

This is the largest room in the compound.  There is no ceiling here and the floor is sand around which is a thick sidewalk.  In the large sandy area, you see multiple stations for various workouts.  There's a yoga station, an area for weight lifting, a long table and some chairs, and a row of dummies for battle training.

You take a chance and slowly creep into the commons area.  You look around and see a gathering of about 50-60 Dingoes near the northwest corner of the room.  They appear to be surrounding a stage and seem quite worked up.  On the stage are two men.  One tall, fit looking man with the evilest of expressions and the other a monster of a man, one of the largest you've ever seen looks beaten and empty.

> look at weight lifting station

> look at weight lifting station
It's nothing like your weight room at home - this one is existent - but it is also not considerably large.  There are some dumbbells of various weights lying about and a bench press here.
You are distracted by the man on stage.  '...and, Dingoes, we are led to this moment!'
> take dumbbells

> take dumbbells
You try and lift a few off the ground and they are too heavy.  You eventually find one that you can sort of lug around.  Twenty five pounds... hmph... about a quarter of your body weight.
